* Version 0.4.9 (11.12.2014)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- add scripts to hibernate, suspend and shutdown, when upower or pm-utils aren't installed
- clean up
- refactoring
- bug fixes

* Version 0.4.7 - (31.10.2014) - https://github.com/nictki/Battmon/releases/0.4.7
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 - add default minimal level battery command
 - add list of screen lock programs, first one will be used as default
 - add shell scripts to hibernate, suspend and shutdown
 - logical fixes
 - small changes

* Version 0.4.3 - (28.10.2013) - https://github.com/nictki/Battmon/releases/0.4.3
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- fix setting process name under python3, thus setproctitle module is not really needed
- removed setproctitle module dependency
- fix unsupported python version check
- and small fixes
- final version

* Version 0.4.2 - (28.10.2013) - https://github.com/nictki/Battmon/releases/0.4.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- bug fixes
- add program version in debug
- add missing arguments in ArgumentError calls
- play sounds when battery has minimal level, even if sound was disabled

* Version 0.4.1 - (27.10.2013) - https://github.com/nictki/Battmon/releases/0.4.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- add 0 prefix to version naming (0.x.x)
- refactoring
- small bug fixes
- fix small logic errors
- add README and CHANGELOG files
- remove README.md file

* Version 3.2.1 - 26.10.2013 - https://github.com/nictki/Battmon/releases/tag/3.2.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- fix behavior in __check_if_running() function

* Version 3.2 - 22.10.2013
---------------------------
- use argparse instead optparse
- new argument names for command line
- bug fixes, refactoring
- fix behavior when battery is removed or inserted
- add notification when battery is removed or inserted
- fix behavior when battery value is 'Unknown'

* Version 3.0.1 - (10.07.2013) - https://github.com/nictki/Battmon/releases/3.0.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- fix upower check
- improve computing current battery capacity
- improve check if battery is full
- fix behavior when battery status is "Unknown"
- make setproctitle module optional
- when both pm-utils and upower are installed, upower will be used as default
- workaround for libc.prctl(15, name, 0, 0, 0) under python3
- fix "run more then one copy" under python2
- python3 is now supported
- program name is set through setproctitle module
- some code cleanup
- update README

* Version 2.1.5.1 - 23.05.2013 - https://github.com/nictki/Battmon/releases/tag/2.1.5.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- small fixes
- add upower check

* Version 2.1 - 07.03.2013
---------------------------
- add check for python correct version
- small fixes
- add option to specify time for "no battery" remainder (default: 0/disabled)
- add option to specify default minimal battery level value action (default: hibernate)

* Version 2.0 - 25.02.2013
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- 2.0-rc4
- get rid of pynotify module, use notify-send instead
- notify-send shows all information, like battery charge time, level etc
- code cleanup
- some improvements
- re-add session lock commands

* Version 1.2 - 26.11.2012
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- improved check if battery is present or not
- added better warnings if some optional dependency is missing
- added sound files to github
- no more acpi or /proc needed, battery percentage and remaining time is read form /sys/class/power_supply
- fixed 'no battery present' loop
- fixed battery and adapter detections
- added pop'ups checking if optional dependencies are installed
- added possibility to fork program in background
- added possibility to run only one copy of program
- minor fixes
